ActPilotage Act
PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING THE PACIFIC PILOTAGE TARIFF REGULATIONS allow the Authority to increase by 3.9% its general tariff for the following pilotage charges: pilotage assignments; time charges for bridge watches and minimum charges; cancellation charges, out-of-region charges, pilot boat and helicopter charges in order to ensure financial self-sufficiency in each individual area.
